flowchart TD
    Start[Storage finding with evidence and coverage]
    Choose{Canonical ActionType}
    Info[Informational path: report-only, open-settings, or manual-instructions]
    Explain[Explain consequence and uncertainty; no CLYR storage mutation]

    Start --> Choose
    Choose -->|report-only / open-settings / manual-instructions| Info
    Info --> Explain

    Choose -->|recycle-files / quarantine-files / trusted-tool-command / windows-supported-cleanup / move-known-folder| Protect{Protected-resource and capability policy}
    Protect -->|Denied or unknown| Prohibited[RiskLevel Prohibited: reject with no override]
    Protect -->|Allowed| Build[Build resolved immutable plan with stable identity evidence]

    Build --> DryRun[Dry run: validate scope, effect, rollback, elevation, and byte qualification]
    DryRun --> Bounded{Exact bounded effect available?}
    Bounded -->|No| ReportOnly[Remain report-only or manual-instructions]
    Bounded -->|Yes| Preview[Display exact plan, consequence, rollback, risk, estimate status, and ten-minute expiry]

    Preview --> Risk{RiskLevel}
    Risk -->|Informational| Explain
    Risk -->|Prohibited| Prohibited
    Risk -->|High without capability-specific approval| Gated[Unavailable pending ADR, threat review, UX review, fixtures, and release approval]
    Risk -->|Low| Select[Explicit opt-in; beta selections start empty]
    Risk -->|Medium| Acknowledge[Separate consequence acknowledgement; no hidden Low batch]
    Select --> Confirm{Confirm displayed plan digest?}
    Acknowledge --> Confirm
    Confirm -->|No| Stop[Stop with zero mutation]
    Confirm -->|Yes| Fresh{Unexpired and materially unchanged?}
    Fresh -->|No| Replan[Invalidate confirmation and create a new dry run]
    Replan --> Build
    Fresh -->|Yes| JournalConfirmed[Persist and flush Confirmed before UAC or execution]
    JournalConfirmed --> Elevation{Approved capability requires elevation?}

    Elevation -->|No| Validate[Validate complete batch again]
    Elevation -->|Yes| UAC{Windows UAC consent}
    UAC -->|Denied| FailedNoChange[Failed attempt with zero mutation]
    UAC -->|Approved| IPC[Authenticate one secure typed IPC session]
    IPC --> Validate

    Validate --> Valid{Every item and target still valid?}
    Valid -->|No| FailedNoChange
    Valid -->|Yes| JournalExecuting[Persist and flush Validating to Executing transition]
    JournalExecuting --> Execute[Executing: perform only compiled approved actions]
    Execute --> Verify[Verifying: target postconditions and before/after free space]
    Verify --> Outcome{Verified transaction outcome}

    Outcome -->|No mutation and failure| Failed[Failed]
    Outcome -->|Some effect, uncertainty, cancellation, or verification failure| Partial[PartiallyCompleted]
    Outcome -->|Verified and no CLYR rollback| Completed[Completed]
    Outcome -->|Verified with recovery path| RollbackAvailable[RollbackAvailable]
    RollbackAvailable --> RollbackPlan[New typed rollback plan and explicit confirmation]
    RollbackPlan --> Rollback[Execute and verify rollback]
    Rollback -->|Verified| RolledBack[RolledBack]
    Rollback -->|Conflict, partial, or unknown| Partial

    Failed --> Receipt[Immutable privacy-safe receipt]
    Partial --> Receipt
    Completed --> Receipt
    RollbackAvailable --> Receipt
    RolledBack --> Receipt
    FailedNoChange --> Receipt
    Receipt --> Report[Report measured bytes separately from the original estimate]

    Phase0[Phase 0 boundary: this workflow is design only; no mutation code exists]
    Phase0 -.-> DryRun
